OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FScattered showers today with
OL,6,Foccasional bright spells in between.
OL,7,FThe showers will be heavy at times
OL,8,Fwith a risk of thunder and hail.
OL,9,FFeeling pleasant in any brighter
OL,10,Fspells with a gentle breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will gradually fade
OL,13,Fthis evening to leave clear spells,
OL,14,Falthough the odd outbreak of rain is
OL,15,Fstill possible at times overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA spell of persistent rain
OL,18,Fspreads across the region during the
OL,19,Fmorning, followed by sunny spells and
OL,20,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
