OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWindy
OL,6,Fon Thursday with blustery showers and
OL,7,Fa risk of thunder. Showers less
OL,8,Ffrequent on Friday. Likely staying
OL,9,Flargely cloudy and dry on Saturday.
OL,10,FFresher than of late.
